ortant writer at the height of her power"--cProvided by publisher.  a43 0aMoneyvFiction. 0aWealthxMoral and ethical aspectsvFiction.  aPS 3552 E53849 A6 2015c1hUAHS-Bi0162035235504  aPS 3552 E53849 A6 2015wLCc1i0162035235504d10/13/2016e10/8/2016lON_SHELFmUAHSSn10p$150.00rYsYtBOOKu2/11/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n99263345bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/36251770